metadata.name: FUCK BEN
metadata.description: FUCK BEN is a Hybrid NFT/MEMECOIN collection that encapsulates the collective fatigue of relentless grifting that we see daily. Each digital piece stands as a visually striking protest against deception from our Lizard Overlords. Each NFT will be your ticket to your MEMECOIN $FBEN allocation that will be based on an upcoming snapshot. Additional bonuses will be distributed for holders with 5, 10 and 20 FUCK BEN NFTs in their wallets. There are 25 1/1's in this collection as well that will earn bonus allocations of $FBEN. Additionally, holding any tokens from $PEPE, $TURBO, $CUT, $RFD, $EGG, $COPE $MONG, $BIAO, $GRDN, $WEN, $JESUS & $DYOR all get you bonus allocations. We've got Ordinals coming too - we'll be working on that, marketing this whole thing and (mostly) playing Diablo 4 all Summer.
